         <abstract id="aspace_f243eb865a1b14f2e72ea342f45b0008">Letters from William Hazlitt to various parties, along with letters by Hazlitt's father (William Hazlitt) and Hazlitt's son (William Hazlitt) as well as three manuscripts by Hazlitt.</abstract>
